00:03:56.247 --> 00:03:59.235
of basketballs you produce by eight,

00:03:59.235 --> 00:04:00.710
so if you add eight basketballs,

00:04:00.710 --> 00:04:04.137
well, you're gonna give
up six pairs of shoes,

