you give up six pairs of
shoes and so in country A

00:04:10.062 --> 00:04:15.031
eight basketballs cost six
shoes, let me write that down,

00:04:15.031 --> 00:04:17.864
so in country A, eight basketballs

00:04:18.816 --> 00:04:20.841
and I'll just say B for short,

00:04:20.841 --> 00:04:22.174
cost six, six S,

00:04:25.822 --> 00:04:27.800
S is shoes for short,

00:04:27.800 --> 00:04:29.011
or another way to think about it,

00:04:29.011 --> 00:04:31.875
if you divide both of these by eight,

00:04:31.875 --> 00:04:33.542
one basketball costs

00:04:34.940 --> 00:04:36.690
six over eight shoes,

