pairs of shoes and so
what is that gonna be?

00:04:47.036 --> 00:04:49.670
Well, six over eight is the
same thing as three fourths

00:04:49.670 --> 00:04:52.142
or three fourths of a pair of shoes,

00:04:52.142 --> 00:04:55.838
so one basketball costs three
fourths of a pair of shoes

00:04:55.838 --> 00:04:58.421
or we could say that as 0.75 S,

00:04:59.779 --> 00:05:02.716
where S is a pair of shoes

00:05:02.716 --> 00:05:04.571
for this is my simplified notation

00:05:04.571 --> 00:05:07.258
and what about in country B?

00:05:07.258 --> 00:05:08.843
Well, in country B,

00:05:08.843 --> 00:05:13.233
if I go from no basketballs
to four basketballs,

00:05:13.233 --> 00:05:16.123
then I would have given
up four pairs of shoes,

00:05:16.123 --> 00:05:18.600
I would have given up four pairs of shoes,

00:05:18.600 --> 00:05:21.183
so in country B, so in B, four,

00:05:23.065 --> 00:05:24.815
four basketballs cost

00:05:26.753 --> 00:05:28.236
four pairs of shoes

00:05:28.236 --> 00:05:31.276
or divide both by four, you
